<P>A DIGEST OF THE PROCEEDINGS OF THE COURT LEET OF THE MANOR AND LIBERTY OF THE <HI>SAVOY,</HI> PARCEL OF THE DUCHY OF LANCASTER, IN THE COUNTY OF MIDDLESEX; FROM THE YEAR 1682 TO THE PRESENT TIME.</P>
<P>PRINTED IN THE YEAR M.DCC.LXXXIX.</P>
